# Light & Dark Mode in Jetpack Compose: Building a Seamless UI
[](/@dinesh.prabha1205?source=post_page---byline--b194eeda7ad0---------------------------------------)[Dinesh N](/@dinesh.prabha1205?source=post_page---byline--b194eeda7ad0---------------------------------------)Follow3 min read·Apr 3, 2025[
